graph-ve-dialog-edit-apply: Label for the apply button in the graph editing dialog
graph-ve-dialog-edit-cancel: Label for the cancel button in the graph editing dialog
graph-ve-dialog-edit-field-raw-json: Label for the raw JSON specification in the graph editing dialog
graph-ve-dialog-edit-json-invalid: Validation label for the JSON specification string
graph-ve-dialog-edit-title: Title for the graph editing dialog
graph-ve-dialog-button-tooltip: Tooltip for the graph editing dialog button
graph-ve-no-spec: Label to display on a graph node when no spec is found
graph-ve-vega-error: Label to display on a graph node when Vega encounters an unknown error
graph-ve-vega-error-no-render: Label to display on a graph node when Vega is unable to render
